        <Parent_String>crayons (drawing material) [300022415], drafting, drawing and writing equipment by specific type [300168215], equipment for drafting, drawing, and writing [300168214], image-making equipment [300162803], equipment by process [300024659], equipment [300122241], Tools and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300022238], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
